{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-plugin-react-css-modules\"><a href=\"#gatsby-plugin-react-css-modules\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-plugin-react-css-modules</h1>\n<p>Transforms <code class=\"language-text\">styleName</code> to <code class=\"language-text\">className</code> using compile time CSS module resolution.\nSee the\n<a href=\"https://github.com/gajus/babel-plugin-react-css-modules/blob/master/README.md\">babel-plugin-react-css-modules README</a>\nfor details.</p>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save gatsby-plugin-react-css-modules</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-plugin-react-css-modules`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// *.css files are included by default.</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// To support another syntax (e.g. SCSS),</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// add `postcss-scss` to your project's devDependencies</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// and add the following option here:</span>\n      filetypes<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\".scss\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> syntax<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`postcss-scss`</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Exclude global styles from the plugin using a RegExp:</span>\n      exclude<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`\\/global\\/`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>Files must be named using the pattern <code class=\"language-text\">filename.module.css</code> for Gatsby to treat\nthem as CSS modules. You can change this behavior using a custom webpack config\n<a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/docs/add-custom-webpack-config/\">https://www.gatsbyjs.org/docs/add-custom-webpack-config/</a></p>","excerpt":"gatsby-plugin-react-css-modules Transforms   to   using compile time CSS module resolution.\nSee the\n babel-plugin-react-css-modules READMEâ€¦","timeToRead":1,"fields":{"title":"gatsby-plugin-react-css-modules"},"parent":{"__typename":"File","relativePath":"gatsby-plugin-react-css-modules/README.md"}},"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-plugin-react-css-modules","keywords":["babel","babel-plugin","className","css modules","gatsby","gatsby-plugin","react","styleName"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"kylemathews","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/e567aa8adbd2d49cd9990ea1ed19d4eb"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-plugin-react-css-modules/","id":"60bda11e-a4b4-50b6-a51a-3e6d8a97e73f"}}